Introduction¶

Overview¶

Selected DataSet :TMDb movie data

This data set contains information about 10,000 movies collected from The Movie Database (TMDb),

Each record has : TMovie ID, imdb ID, popularity, budget, revenue, original title, cast, homepage, director, tagline, overview, runtime, genres, production companies, release date, vote count, vote average, release year, budget adj, revenue adj

Question that will be solved:¶

1- What is the most loved Generes?

2- Is there a relation between the movie success and the Run time?

3- what is the most proftiable year quarter ? the year has 4 quarters and every quarter last for 3 months

def seperate_col_to_rows(df,col,separator,id):
    """Return the dataframe after seperating the col with the separator to new rows indexing by id """
    #transfer list to rows after seperation
    df=df.copy()
    new_df = pd.DataFrame(df[col].str.split(separator).tolist(),index=df[id]).stack()
    #reset index using id
    new_df = new_df.reset_index([0, id])
    new_df.columns=[id,col]
    #drop old col
    df.drop([col],axis=1,inplace=True)
    #merge new col with the dataset 
    df=pd.merge(df,new_df,how='inner',left_on=id, right_on=id)
    
    return df

#seprate genre col to rows 
tmdb_genre=seperate_col_to_rows(tmdb,'genres','|','id')

Research Question 3 (what is the most proftiable year quarter ?)¶

In [121]:
tmdb_season=tmdb.loc[:,['release_date','revenue']]
tmdb_season.head()
q1=tmdb_season[(tmdb_season['release_date'].dt.month >= 1 )& (tmdb_season['release_date'].dt.month <= 3)]
q2=tmdb_season[(tmdb_season['release_date'].dt.month >= 4 )& (tmdb_season['release_date'].dt.month <= 6)]
q3=tmdb_season[(tmdb_season['release_date'].dt.month >= 7 )& (tmdb_season['release_date'].dt.month <= 9)]
q4=tmdb_season[(tmdb_season['release_date'].dt.month >= 10 )& (tmdb_season['release_date'].dt.month <= 12)]

q1=q1.sum()
q2=q2.sum()
q3=q3.sum()
q4=q4.sum()
tmdb_season=pd.DataFrame(data=[['q1', q1['revenue']], ['q2', q2['revenue']],['q3', q3['revenue']], ['q4', q4['revenue']]],columns=['quarter','revene_total'])
